	Set-3parVV -Name as2 -RO
	
  .EXAMPLE	
	Set-3parVV -Name as2 -Force -RemoveAndRecreate 
	
  .PARAMETER Name 
    Specifies the name(s) of the snapshot virtual volume(s) or virtual volume set(s) to be updated.

